|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031025231430/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/3212185.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，他早前在以0-1不敵[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]的賽事已經膝部受傷<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 |url        = http://archive.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/2003/10/20/106651.html
 |title      = An away-day horror show
 |date       = 20 October 2003
 |accessdate = 2008-02-05
 |publisher  = ''Telegraph & Argus''
