|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/3363781.stm
|title=Norwich 0-1 Bradford
|date=10 January 2004
|accessdate=2008-02-08
|publisher=BBC Sport
|archive-date=2004-06-17
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040617110839/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/3363781.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。然而，這次復出是很短暫的—他的小腿受傷，儘管這次他只錯過了一場賽事<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
