|first=Dean
|title=From Gipsyville to the Premiership
|url=https://archive.org/details/deano0000wind
|publisher=Great Northern
|year=2007
|isbn=978-1-905080-29-8
|page=[https://archive.org/details/deano0000wind/page/125 125]}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 |url        = http://archive.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/2003/11/21/105558.html
 |title      = Jacobs: City are my dream team
 |date       = 21 November 2003
 |accessdate = 2008-02-05
 |publisher  = ''Telegraph & Argus''
}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2007年2月12日，隨著{{Link-en|哥連·鐸|Colin Todd}}被巴拉福特解僱後，韋瑟羅爾首次被任命為球員兼領隊並以代理領隊形式全面執掌球會<ref name="todd">{{en}}{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/6354497.stm
|title=Bradford part company with Todd
|date=12 February 2007
|accessdate=2008-02-05
|publisher=BBC Sport
|archive-date=2007-02-22
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222003551/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/6354497.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。雖然，球會的表現並不好<ref name="todd"/> ，但是他的職位獲保留直到3月<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/6444657.stm
|title=Wetherall to stay on as caretaker
|date=13 March 2007
|accessdate=2008-02-05
|publisher=BBC Sport
|archive-date=2007-03-15
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070315203606/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/6444657.stm
